text: Trash Truck s an American animated television series. It was created and written by Max Keane. It revolves around the adventures of a young boy named Hank and his best friend Trash Truck who is a garbage truck. It premiered on November 10, 2020 on Netflix. A second season premiered on May 4, 2021.
